HCC -- HACK Compiler Collection
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

This is an effort to make the best available toolchain for HACK computer
platform, as described in the book The Elements of Computing Systems,
available at http://www1.idc.ac.il/tecs/

INSTALLATION
~~~~~~~~~~~~
To install, issue command
    # make
in this directory. Optionally, do
    # make test
as well. Then copy compiled executables from directory "src" to any
directory in your $PATH, e.g.
    # cp src/hcc-{vm,asm,emulator,vm2hack} ~/bin
